% Erlang Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with Erlang-specific concepts

% File/Module types
Every erlang-compilation-unit is a compilation-unit.
Every erlang-module is a module.

% Type definitions
Every erlang-record is a struct.
Every erlang-behaviour is an interface.

% Members
Every erlang-function is a function.
Every erlang-field is a field.

% Parameters
Every erlang-parameter is a parameter.

% Import
Every erlang-import is an import.
Every erlang-include is an import.

% Exception handling
Every erlang-try-block is a try-block.
Every erlang-catch-clause is a catch-clause.
Every erlang-finally-clause is a finally-clause.
Every erlang-throw-statement is a throw-statement.

% Control flow
Every erlang-return-statement is a return-statement.

% Other
Every erlang-variable is a variable.
Every erlang-reference is a reference.
Every erlang-anonymous-function is an anonymous-function.

% Erlang-Specific Concepts
Every erlang-export is an export.
Every erlang-type-spec is a type-def.
Every erlang-macro is a macro.

% Code Smells
Every erlang-long-function is a long-method.
